name: Portraits of the Non-Existent : 04 : RON
description: Blending my own anthropomorphic biases with multiple levels of pseudofigurative-artificial intelligence-generated imagery, I create what I could best describe as {yet to be categorized} art to be enjoyed by [humans, machines, and everything/one] in between.
